title: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince Audio Book
description:
Book 6. Harry Potter & the Half-Blood Prince

Organized

Good Quality (160 KBPS) (I beleive)

Ripped from CDs

Read by Jim Dale

Seed....

This is definetely my favorite of the Harry Potter Series. By far, book seven is next in line.
They're all amazing, but i think this one was always my favorite.
By the way these files work amazing on an ipod. Some MP3 players dont work as well because they will try to organize them numerically. and since i didn't put a zero in front of the single digit chapters they organize them like so....

1.
10.
11.
12.
13.
and so on.
2.
20.
21.
Yeah its a pain. Windows Media player does something like that too only worse. So even if you don't own an ipod, I still recomend using iTunes to play these. It is the best for them i think.
